      "value": "<p><strong>Access</strong> You are a member of the College of Mysteries</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your face bears an intricate magical tattoo known as the <em>irezoko</em>, a badge of your understanding of your chosen field of magic and a recognition of your advancement within Absalom's College of Mysteries. Choose a class that you are a member of that grants you access to a focus pool. When you take this feat, it gains the trait that applies to your chosen class. Once per day, you may concentrate upon the pattern of your <em>irezoko</em> to recover 1 Focus Point as a three-action activity.</p>"
